snippet.title: Vampire: The Masquerade - Bloodhunt - Pre-Order Available | PS5
snippet.description:
https://www.playstation.com/en-us/games/vampire-the-masquerade-bloodhunt/

Roam the city of Prague and dominate the night thanks to the next-gen features of the PlayStation 5! The DualSense adaptive triggers bring the player at the heart of the battle, while 3D audio gives them a competitive advantage over their opponents. Pre-order now to receive exclusive rewards at launch, on April 27th. 

Rated Mature
